1. *Shvatili* smo da je ovo teško zadatak. (We understood that this is a difficult task.)
2. Oni su *shvatili* da ne mogu da menjaju događaje. (They realized that they can't change the events.) 
3. *Shvatili* smo koliko je značajno biti zahvalan. (We realized how important it is to be grateful.)
4. Oni su *shvatili* da moraju da razumeju jedni druge. (They understood that they had to understand each other.)
5. *Shvatili* smo da je ovo bila veoma važna odluka. (We understood that this was a very important decision.)